original_title: How I Met My Girlfriend Chanel Preston
overview: Hitting on Chanel Preston, your super hot boss, isn't the best idea... if you want to stay in office. But if you don't, you've got the green light to ask Chanel out on a super unusual first date: you're going hiking! Who knows, if you do it right, you might get a second date.
title: How I Met My Girlfriend Chanel Preston
